<!--

  Challenge:
  
    id              = track ID
    type            = {racing | freestyle | crash }
    leaderboard_id  = leaderboard stat view ID
    context_id      = context ID
    fullonly        = true if not in trial mode, false if available in trial mode
    difficulty      = 1 (beginner), 2 (easy), 3 (medium), 4 (hard), 5 (inferno)
    factor          = fault factor for global csore calculation

    Limits:

      pass          = minimum time to pass track (milliseconds)
      gold,         = in racing mode, times to reach medals in this track (milliseconds)
      silver,         in other modes, points to reach medals in this track
      bronze
      
      pass_faults,  = maximum faults to pass this medal
      gold_faults,
      silver_faults,
      bronze_faults

-->
